OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776881467
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CMalcolm Offord leader interview
OL,6,FITV Border will be sitting down with
OL,7,Fall the main political party leaders
OL,8,Fduring the Holyrood election campaign.
OL,10,FThe fourth interview was with Reform
OL,11,FUK's Malcolm Offord. Here are three
OL,12,Fthings we learned.
OL,14,FHe's been on a journey
OL,16,FIn Malcolm Offord's first speech as a
OL,17,Fparliamentarian, his debut on the red
OL,18,Fbenches as Lord Offord of Garvel, he
OL,19,Fsaid the UK has "the capital, the
OL,20,Fbrains and the political will to meet
OL,21,Fthe climate challenge".
OL,26,@{D@QOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
