CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776881467
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CMalcolm Offord leader interview
OL,6,FNow he says it is a "fatuous question"
OL,7,Fto ask whether climate change is real.
OL,9,FHe said: "It's a question that people
OL,10,Fseem to get hung up on. The science.
OL,11,FWhat is the science?
OL,13,F"Science is always disputed. For me
OL,14,Fit's not an ideological thing. We want
OL,15,Fto have the cleanest possible system.
OL,17,F"We want to be environmentally aware,
OL,18,Fwe want to hand over the planet in the
OL,19,Fbest possible way to the next
OL,20,Fgeneration. There's no question about
OL,21,Fthat."
OL,26,@nD@UOUnD@fO]qD@JOUuD@AOUyD@AOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
