PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776881467
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CMalcolm Offord leader interview
OL,6,FMr Offord added: "The world heats up
OL,7,Fand cools down. And heats up and cools
OL,8,Fdown. So I don't want to get into that
OL,9,Fargument about science."
OL,11,FHe said he was never "enthusiastic"
OL,12,Fand that he simply "read the lines I
OL,13,Fwas given" as a minister, which
OL,14,Fcritics have suggested is not the best
OL,15,Fimpression to give as a party leader.
OL,17,FHe also said there was little the UK
OL,18,Fcould do because "we account for less
OL,19,Fthan 1% of global emissions: 0.81%.
OL,20,FChina accounts for 30%. The US for
OL,21,F13%".
OL,26,@nD@ROUqD@XO]sD@VOUsD@cO]tD@TOUuD@JO]zD@
OL,26,AROU}D@DO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
