OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776881467
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CMalcolm Offord leader interview
OL,6,FBack in 2022, he told the Lords in
OL,7,Fthat maiden speech: "Some say that the
OL,8,FUK has a limited role to play in
OL,9,Fclimate change as we account for only
OL,10,F1 per cent of world emissions. Yet
OL,11,FCOP26 proved our leadership still
OL,12,Fcounts as we show it is possible to
OL,13,Fsimultaneously grow our economy whilst
OL,14,Fcutting our emissions."
OL,16,FHe also says now that while he remains
OL,17,Fin favour of controlled immigration,
OL,18,Fhe has shifted his view on the impact
OL,19,Fof asylum seekers on communities.
OL,26,@oD@UOUvD@WO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/15
