CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776881467
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CMalcolm Offord leader interview
OL,6,FMr Offord once referred to himself as
OL,7,F"reluctant Brexiteer" but is now much
OL,8,Fmore enthusiastic about the UK having
OL,9,Fleft the European Union.
OL,11,F"Isn't that a good thing to learn," he
OL,12,Fsaid. "Isn't that what life's all
OL,13,Fabout? To learn more, to inform
OL,14,Fyourself."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@UO]sD@AOUsD@cO]tD@GOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776881467
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CMalcolm Offord leader interview
OL,6,F"What is it Maynard Keating said that
OL,7,Fwhen the facts change, I change my
OL,8,Fmind. I haven't changed my mind on any
OL,9,Fof these things. What I've done is
OL,10,Fstrengthened my position and I've
OL,11,Fstrengthened my position by being
OL,12,Finformed."
OL,14,FHe really wants to pick a fight with
OL,15,FAnas Sarwar... and Tommy Robinson
OL,17,FSometimes things happen in an
OL,18,Finterview that surprise you even after
OL,19,F18 years as a journalist.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@JO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
