OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CMalcolm Offord leader interview
OL,6,FA party political leader pulling a
OL,7,Fflash card from his inside pocket that
OL,8,Fcontains quotes from one of his rivals
OL,9,Fis this kind of moment.
OL,11,FMr Offord had a list of statements
OL,12,Fmade by Anas Sarwar in a speech a few
OL,13,Fyears ago.
OL,15,FThat speech formed the basis of an
OL,16,Fattack advert by Reform that falsely
OL,17,Fclaimed the Scottish Labour leader
OL,18,F"has said he will prioritise the
OL,19,FPakistani community."
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776881467
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CMalcolm Offord leader interview
OL,6,FMr Offord said it was "not necessarily
OL,7,Flanguage I would have used but what
OL,8,FI'm clear about is that if a speech is
OL,9,Fmade by any politician, those words
OL,10,Fcan be used and that is a legitimate
OL,11,Fexercise."
OL,13,FChallenged over the fact Mr Sarwar did
OL,14,Fnot say the words in the Reform
OL,15,Fadvert, Mr Offord produced a card from
OL,16,Fhis jacket pocket of "other things
OL,17,Fthat he said in that speech."
OL,26,@nD@WOUxD@VOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776881467
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CMalcolm Offord leader interview
OL,6,FMr Offord said: "So what he said in
OL,7,Fhis speech was, he said the following.
OL,8,F"He said: 'The days when South Asian
OL,9,Fcommunities get to lead political
OL,10,Fparties and get to lead countries is
OL,11,Fupon us'."
OL,13,FAsked if that was a bad thing, Mr
OL,14,FOfford added: "I'm just giving you
OL,15,Fthat for context. And the second thing
OL,16,Fhe said, which I would like to
OL,17,Fquestion him on, was: 'The days where
OL,18,FSouth Asian communities get to decide
OL,19,Fnot just which school our children go
OL,20,Fto but what they are taught in these
OL,21,Fschools is also coming'."
OL,26,@nD@QOUpD@AOUsD@JO]}D@YO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776881467
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CMalcolm Offord leader interview
OL,6,FThis led to Mr Sarwar accusing Mr
OL,7,FOfford of trying to "race-bait" him
OL,8,Fduring the election campaign.
OL,10,FYou might expect a party to back away
OL,11,Ffrom that. Instead Mr Offord promoted
OL,12,Fa social media post from his party
OL,13,Fcolleague Thomas Kerr that contained
OL,14,Fthe above exchange and said: "Anas
OL,15,FSarwar should not be immune to
OL,16,Fscrutiny. Reform will continue to
OL,17,Fhighlight his divisive language and
OL,18,Fhold him accountable."
OL,26,@oD@UOUoD@_O]vD@^OU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776881467
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CMalcolm Offord leader interview
OL,6,FBut unlike some of his candidates, Mr
OL,7,FOfford was firm in his rejection of
OL,8,Fthe far right activist Tommy Robinson,
OL,9,Fwhose real name is Stephen Yaxley-
OL,10,FLennon.
OL,12,FMr Offord said there is "no common
OL,13,Fground between Tommy Robinson and
OL,14,FReform".
OL,16,FAsked if he had told his candidates to
OL,17,Fstop endorsing Robinson, he was
OL,18,Fcrystal clear.
OL,20,F"Yeah, absolutely. Yes, yes, yes."
OL,26,@tD@YOUvD@GO]|D@AOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776881467
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CMalcolm Offord leader interview
OL,6,FHe thinks Reform's support base is
OL,7,Fwidening
OL,9,FReform's support base has mostly come
OL,10,Ffrom "left behind" towns.
OL,12,FSometimes in parts of cities that feel
OL,13,Fthe same way but, crucially, it has
OL,14,Fmostly been an urban phenomenon.
OL,16,FNot any more, claims Mr Offord.
OL,26,@rD@FOUrD@RO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776881467
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CMalcolm Offord leader interview
OL,6,FHe said: "South of Scotland is a very
OL,7,Fstrong area for us. Obviously you've
OL,8,Fgot a certain number of working towns
OL,9,Fin the south but you've also got a
OL,10,Fvery big rural community and that's
OL,11,Fwhere we're getting a lot of traction,
OL,12,Fwith farmers, with farm workers etc.
OL,14,F"There's been a bit of an attack on
OL,15,Ffarms recently by the Labour
OL,16,Fgovernment certainly at Westminster.
OL,26,@nD@JOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776881467
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CMalcolm Offord leader interview
OL,6,F"I've made it a very, very hard
OL,7,Ftarget. And then this idea of the SNP
OL,8,Ftrying to cap the price of milk and
OL,9,Fkey foodstuffs will be a disaster
OL,10,Faround here.
OL,12,F"So we've got a strong group of
OL,13,Fsupport here."
OL,15,FReform UK has its eye on at least two
OL,16,Fconstituencies in the South of
OL,17,FScotland, as well as hoping to make a
OL,18,Fbig impact on the regional list.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/15
